We plead the blood of Jesus Christ over every single body that's represented here—all cancer, all diabetes, all heart disease, all lung disease, all kidney disease, all anything that's attached to their body satanically, we take authority over it right now in the name of Jesus.

00:20:55.070 --> 00:21:02.611
We call healing over their minds, over their stomachs, over their serotonin levels, over their dopamine, over anything that they need.

00:21:02.611 --> 00:21:08.199
We call deliverance and healing and wholeness and wellness over them in the name of Jesus.

00:21:08.199 --> 00:21:14.165
We speak to PTSD; we call healing over PTSD in the name of Jesus.

00:21:14.165 --> 00:21:19.180
We call deliverance from drug addictions right now—opioid addictions, we call you delivered in the name of Jesus.

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:31.846
From all kinds of blood disorders—from AIDS, from hepatitis, from sexually transmitted diseases—we call you healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:36.756
We call you delivered from those things.

00:21:40.080 --> 00:21:45.530
We call for new kidneys; we call kidney disease healed and whole and well right now in the name of Jesus.

00:21:50.742 --> 00:21:53.658
A brand new kidney is coming to you right now.

00:21:53.658 --> 00:22:05.428
We call complete restoration of your kidneys, complete restoration of your liver, complete restoration of your thyroid, complete restoration of your pancreas.

00:22:05.428 --> 00:22:12.267
All diabetes, type one and type two, we call healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:22:12.267 --> 00:22:24.439
We call marriages restored, hearts to be healed and whole and well in Jesus' name, and we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it right now in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:22:24.439 --> 00:22:27.672
Well, I just want to say thank you for joining me.

00:22:27.672 --> 00:22:31.286
I know that was a heavy word, but that's what I got.

00:22:31.530 --> 00:22:34.180
I feel in my heart I need to warn you.

00:22:34.180 --> 00:22:41.859
When the Holy Spirit is warning me and showing me things coming, I'm trying to tell you there's a storm coming.

00:22:41.859 --> 00:22:49.120
I'm trying to tell you there's a great shaking coming, and people are asleep and they don't see it coming.

00:22:49.120 --> 00:22:56.955
Their hearts are hardened to the things of God, and God's calling you to repent and get your life right before Him.

00:22:56.955 --> 00:23:00.960
Jesus is coming soon, and the bride is asleep.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:05.750
People are not ready for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, and He's coming soon.

00:23:06.060 --> 00:23:10.376
You need to get your heart right before Him or you're going to get left.

00:23:10.376 --> 00:23:23.535
Jesus is coming, and I try to tell you this with all the energy that I have: you better get your heart right, you better get your life right, or you're going to get left.

00:23:23.535 --> 00:23:28.053
Turn or burn—you're running out of time.

00:23:28.053 --> 00:23:31.960
So put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:23:31.960 --> 00:23:35.320
Jesus loves you, and we love you, and we will see you next time.

00:23:35.320 --> 00:23:37.200
You all have a blessed day.

00:23:37.200 --> 00:23:39.920
God bless you all.

00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:40.600
